title: Doctor Qi, your confused baby is crying again
overview: Jiang Xiaoning is a young girl obsessed with studying. At 21, she has already acquired many diplomas, but she doesn't even think about marriage. Qi Yinli is the heir to the Qi family, dedicated to his career as a doctor, completely indifferent to the opposite sex. Their parents secretly marry them in the hope that the young people will fall in love with each other. But they don't even want to get acquainted, they only want a divorce. But fate has already taken a strong hold of them.
